title: [Rumor Woods, Canine Track]
[Rumor Woods, Equid Track]
description: Tall bales of hay litter between the freshly cut stumps of the the area, the grass flanked by a plethora of horseshoes, bits, and buckets of feed.  Loud whinnies seem to echo from behind a wide door, followed by the hammering of iron upon iron, and the sharp whistling from a far away stall.
paths: Obvious paths: north, northeast, east, northwest
